com.zebra.sdk.zxp.job

Interface JobControlHelperUtilZxp


  • public interface JobControlHelperUtilZxp
    Interface for configuring job related parameters.
    • JobControl settings are not persistent across jobs, therefore they must be set for each job.

        Returns:
        the monochrome conversion type.
